    var categoriasEmDestaquePagina     = 0;
    var categoriasEmDestaquePorPagina  = 4;
    var categoriasEmDestaqueQtdPaginas = Math.floor((lotesEmDestaque.length / categoriasEmDestaquePorPagina) + 
            ( lotesEmDestaque.length % categoriasEmDestaquePorPagina == 0?0:1));
    var carouselDestaque;

    // -- init dinamic elements --
    $(function() {
        // init carousel - banner
        var carousel = $("#bannerCarousel");
        carousel.owlCarousel({
            slideSpeed: 400,
            singleItem: true,
            autoPlay: 5000,
            stopOnHover: true
        });

        carouselDestaque = $("#destaqueCarousel");
        carouselDestaque.owlCarousel({
            scrollPerPage: true
        });
        $('#destaqueNext').on('click', function() {
            carouselDestaque.trigger('owl.next');
        });
        $('#destaquePrev').on('click', function() {
            carouselDestaque.trigger('owl.prev');
        });                

        // novo por aqui
        $('#secTour .tourItem').on('mouseenter', function(evt) {
            var divId = $(this).data('tourorder');
            left = $(this).position().left - $('.outerwrapper').offset().left;
            var div = $("#" + divId);
            $(this).css('background-image', 'none');
            div.css('left',left);
            div.stop().show(300);
        }).on('mouseleave', function(evt) {
            var divId = $(this).data('tourorder');
            var div = $("#" + divId);
            $(this).css('background-image', "url('assets/images/novo/mais-icone.png')");
            div.stop().hide(300);
        });

        // handle click on item
        $('#secProximos .landingRow article').on('click', function(evt) {
            var url = $(this).find('a').attr('href');
            location = url;
        });
        $('#secProximos .landingRow article').on('mouseover', function(evt) {
            $(this).find('figure ul li img').each(function(i){ 
                $(this).attr('src', $(this).data('src'));
                
                $('#secBanner').on('mouseout', function(evt){$('#carouselControls').hide(0);});
                $('#secBanner').on('mouseover', function(evt){$('#carouselControls').show(0);});
            });
        });
//        $('#destaqueCarousel .destaque-item').on('click', function(evt) {
//            var url = $(this).find('a').attr('href');
//            window.open(url);
//        });

        // loop trought all logos
        $('.comitenteLogos').owlCarousel({
            singleItem: true,
            autoPlay: true,
            pagination: false,
            navigation: false,
            transitionStyle : "fadeUp",
            rewindNav: true
        });
        /*
        $('#secBanner').on('mouseout', function(evt){$('#carouselControls').hide(0);});
        $('#secBanner').on('mouseover', function(evt){$('#carouselControls').show(0);});
*/
        fillCategories();
        reloadFeaturedCategories();
        reloadFeaturedEvents();
        
        
        var p = '';
        var m = '';
        var link = site_url("main/newsletter/?") + p + m;

        show_popup(link, null);
        $('.popup_overlay').css('opacity', '.85');
        
                            
    });


    // -- util functions --
    function fillCategories() {
        $.each(lotesEmDestaque, function(key, value) {
            $('#secDestaque ul').append('<li data-idcategoria="' + value.idCategoria + '">' + value.nome + '</li>');
        });                
        $('#secDestaque ul').append('<li class="desCatMais" data-idcategoria="0">veja mais opções</li>');
    }

    function reloadFeaturedCategories() {
//                $('#secDestaque ul').empty();
        if(categoriasEmDestaquePagina >= categoriasEmDestaqueQtdPaginas) {
            categoriasEmDestaquePagina = 0;
        }
        var initialIndex = (categoriasEmDestaquePagina * categoriasEmDestaquePorPagina);
        var maxIndex     = initialIndex + categoriasEmDestaquePorPagina;
        $.each(lotesEmDestaque, function(key, value) {
            if(key >= initialIndex && key < maxIndex ) {
                $('#secDestaque ul li:eq(' + key + ')').removeClass('hidden');
            } else {
                $('#secDestaque ul li:eq(' + key + ')').addClass('hidden');
            }
        });
        $('#secDestaque ul li:eq(' + (categoriasEmDestaquePagina * categoriasEmDestaquePorPagina) + ')').trigger('click');
    }  

    function reloadFeaturedEvents() {
        $('#secDestaque ul li.desCatMais').on('click', function(evt) {
            categoriasEmDestaquePagina++;
            reloadFeaturedCategories();
        });

        $('#secDestaque ul li:not(.desCatMais)').on('click', function(evt) {
            idCategoria = $(evt.currentTarget).data('idcategoria');
            $('#destaqueCarousel').empty();                                    
            $.each(lotesEmDestaque, function(key, value) {
                if(value.idCategoria == idCategoria) {
                    $.each(value.lotes, function(key2, value2) {
                        var template = $('#templateFeaturedLote').html();
                        template = template.replace('%%IMG%%', '<img src="' + value2.image + '" />');
                        template = template.replace('%%DESC%%', value2.descricao);
                        template = template.replace('%%LINK%%', 'http://www.sold.com.br/lote/ver' + "/" + value2.idLote);
                        template = template.replace('%%VALUE%%', value2.valorInicial);
                        $('#destaqueCarousel').append(template);
                    });
                    return false;
                }
            });

            // init carousel - itens destaque
            carouselDestaque.data('owlCarousel').reinit({
                slideSpeed: 400,
                items: 3
            });
            // click
            $("#destaqueCarousel .destaque-item").on('click', function(evt) {
                window.open($(this).find('a').attr('href'));
            });
        });
        $('#secDestaque ul li:eq(' + (categoriasEmDestaquePagina * categoriasEmDestaquePorPagina) + ')').trigger('click');
    }
            
</script>
        <script type="text/javascript">
            /* GLOBAL VARS */
            // -- menu control variables  --
            // is mouse, over a menu button?
            var overMenu = false;
            // is mouse, over an open box?
            var overBox  = false;
            // time out to stop menu hidding itself
            var timeoutMenu;
            // keeping button light on
            var buttonLight;
            var buttonOld;
            // content objects
            var arMenuContents = [];  

            // fixed menu
            var nav = $('.nav-container');
            var pos = nav.offset().top;
            
            jQuery("document").ready(function($){

                // extension point
                if(typeof jsPreExecute === 'function') {
                    jsPreExecute();
                }
                
                // fixed menu
                $(window).scroll(function () {
                    var fix = ($(this).scrollTop() > pos) ? true : false;
                    var openMenuTop = 137 + $(this).scrollTop();
                    $('#openMenu').css('top', openMenuTop);
                    nav.toggleClass("fix-nav", fix);
                    $('body').toggleClass("fix-body", fix);
                });              

                // menus
                loadMenu();
                $('#secMainMenu nav ul li').on('mouseenter', function(evt) {
                    if(buttonOld) {
                        menuButtonTurnOff(buttonOld);
                        buttonOld = null;
                    }
                    clearTimeout(timeoutMenu);
                    buttonLight = $(this);
                    // loads menu content
                    var catID = buttonLight.data('categoryid');
                    if(!arMenuContents[catID]) {
                        // loads ajax
                        $.ajax({
                            url: site_url('/main/featuredCategory/' + catID),
                            type: 'GET',
                            cache: false,
                            dataType: 'html',
                            success: function(data) {
                                arMenuContents[catID] = data;
                                $('#openMenu').html(data);
                            }
                        });
                    } else {
                        $('#openMenu').html(arMenuContents[catID]);
                    }
                    var menuPosition = buttonLight.data('openmenuleft');
                    menuButtonTurnOn();
                    var openMenu = $('#openMenu');
                    openMenu.css('left', menuPosition + $('.outerwrapper').offset().left);
                    openMenu.stop().show(200, function() {
                        $(this).css('height','auto');
                    });
                    overMenu = true;
                });
                $('#secMainMenu nav ul li').on('mouseleave', function(evt) {
                    buttonOld = $(this);
                    timeoutMenu = setTimeout(function() {
                        overMenu = false;
                        shouldICloseBox();
                        menuButtonTurnOff(buttonOld);
                        buttonOld = null;
                    }, 500);
                });
                $('#openMenu').on('mouseenter', function(evt) {
                    clearTimeout(timeoutMenu);
                    overBox = true;
                });
                $('#openMenu').on('mouseleave', function(evt) {
                    overBox = false;
                    overMenu = false;
                    shouldICloseBox();
                    menuButtonTurnOff(buttonOld);
                });
                
                $('#openMenu ul.localidade li').on('mouseover', function(evt) {
                    $(this).find('.submenu').css('display', 'block');
                });    
                
                // newsletter - uf combos
                $('#newsUF').change(function(e) {
                    e.preventDefault();

                    if($('#newsUF').val() != "") {
                        $('#wrapper_news_cidade').html('<span class="branco">Carregando...</span>');
                        $('#wrapper_news_cidade').load('http://www.sold.com.br/main/comboCidades'+'/'+$('#newsUF').val() + "/newsCidade");
                    } else {
                        $('#news_cidade').empty();
                        $('#news_cidade').next().html('CIDADE');
                    }
                });
                // handle newsletter form validation
                $('#newsletter').on('submit', function(evt) {
                    if(evt) {
                        evt.preventDefault();
                    }
                    var errorMsg = "";
                    var email = $('#newsEmail').val();
                    var re = /^([\w-]+(?:\.[\w-]+)*)@((?:[\w-]+\.)*\w[\w-]{0,66})\.([a-z]{2,6}(?:\.[a-z]{2})?)$/i;
                    if(!re.test(email)) {
                        errorMsg += "E-mail inválido\n";
                    }
                    if($('#newsUF').val() === "-1") {
                        errorMsg += "Selecione o estado\n";
                    }
                    if($('#newsCidade').val() === "-1") {
                        errorMsg += "Selecione a cidade\n";
                    }
                    if(errorMsg != "") {
                        alert("Verifique os seguintes erros:\n" + errorMsg);
                        return false;
                    }
                    $.post('http://www.sold.com.br/main/assinar_news', {'email':email, 'uf':$('#newsUF').val(), 'cidade':$('#newsCidade').val()}, function(r) {
                        alert(r.message);
                        if(r.result==true) {

                            // Conversão por evento
                            var _gaq = _gaq || [];

                            _gaq.push(['_setAccount', 'UA-22129990-1']);
                            _gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'News', 'Add', 'Cadastro News']);
                            _gaq.push(['_trackPageview']);					

                            // Conversão do AdWords
                            $("#footer_adWordsConversion").attr("src","//www.googleadservices.com/pagead/conversion/1014545539/?value=0&amp;label=kpmDCP3tmQIQg_ni4wM&amp;guid=ON&amp;script=0");

                            /* Facebook Conversion Page */
                            var fb_param = {};
                            fb_param.pixel_id = '6005961757006';
                            fb_param.value = '0.00';
                            (function(){
                              var fpw = document.createElement('script');
                              fpw.async = true;
                              fpw.src = (location.protocol=='http:'?'http':'https')+'://connect.facebook.net/en_US/fp.js';
                              var ref = document.getElementsByTagName('script')[0];
                              ref.parentNode.insertBefore(fpw, ref);
                            })();

                            $('newsEmail').val('');
                        }
                    });
                    return true;
                });
                
                // busca
                $("#frmBusca button").click(buscar);

                $("#busca").keypress(function(e){
                    if(e.keyCode == 13) {
                        buscar();
                    }
                });
                
                // próximos leilões
                $("a#link_prox_leiloes").on('click', function(e) {
                    targetOffset = $("#secProximos").offset().top - 140;
                    e.preventDefault();
                    $("html, body").animate({scrollTop: targetOffset}, 400);
                });
                // checa pelo hash dos próximos leiloes
                if(window.location.hash != "") {
                    $("a#link_prox_leiloes").trigger('click');
                }
                
                
                // extension point
                if(typeof jsPosExecute === 'function') {
                    jsPosExecute();
                }
                
            });
          
            function loadMenu() {
                                arMenuContents[0]  = atob("");
                arMenuContents[1]  = atob("");
                arMenuContents[2]  = atob("");
                arMenuContents[3]  = atob("");
                arMenuContents[4]  = atob("");
                arMenuContents[5]  = atob("");
                arMenuContents[6]  = atob("");
                arMenuContents[7]  = atob("");
                arMenuContents[8]  = atob("");
                arMenuContents[9]  = atob("");
                arMenuContents[10] = atob("");
                arMenuContents[11] = atob("");
            }
          
            /**
             * Checks if category menu should be kept opened
             * @returns void
             */
            function shouldICloseBox() {
                if(!overBox && !overMenu) {
                    $('#openMenu').stop().hide(200);
                }
            }
            
            /**
             * Turns on category menu element
             * @param Element el
             * @returns void
             */
            function menuButtonTurnOn(el) {
                if(el === undefined) el = buttonLight;
                if(el !== undefined) {
                    el.find("span").addClass('menuBlockSpan-on');
                    el.addClass('menuBlock-on');
                    var classe = el.data('onclass');
                    var elFigure = el.find('figure');
                    elFigure.removeClass(classe);
                    elFigure.addClass(classe + "-on");
                }
            }
            
            /**
             * Turns off category menu element
             * @param Element el
             * @returns void
             */
            function menuButtonTurnOff(el) {
                if(el === undefined) el = buttonLight;
                if(el !== undefined) {
                    var classe = el.data('onclass');
                    var elFigure = el.find('figure');
                    elFigure.removeClass(classe + "-on");
                    elFigure.addClass(classe);
                    el.removeClass('menuBlock-on');
                    el.find("span").removeClass('menuBlockSpan-on');
                }
            }
            
            /**
             * Insere um texto no meio de outro
             * @param int index Indice de onde será inserido o texto
             * @param String string Texto a ser inserido
             * @returns {String.prototype@call;substring|String.prototype}
             */
            String.prototype.insert = function (index, string) {
              if (index > 0)
                return this.substring(0, index) + string + this.substring(index, this.length);
              else
                return string + this;
            };
            
            
            function buscar(e){
                if(e) {
                    e.preventDefault();
                }

                var url = '';
                if(!is_empty($("#busca").val())) {
                    var d = $("#busca").val().replace( /[^\wáéíóúäëïöüâêîôûàèìòùãẽĩõũç\'\" ]+/gi, '');
                    url += '/busca/' + encodeURIComponent(d);
                }

                // log da busca
                var dados = { busca : d };
                $.post(
                    "http://www.sold.com.br/lote/log_busca",
                    dados
                );

                window.location = 'http://www.sold.com.br/lote/lista' + url;
            }
            
        </script>
    </body>
